<div class="project-header">
  <h2>Tartan Literary &amp; Arts Magazine Issue 66</h2>
  <span class="project-year">2019</span>
</div>

<div class="project-body">
  <p>I spent my early years of design experience laying out spreads for community magazines around Dallas. The Tartan's 66th Annual Issue was the first publication where I had the opportunity to exercise full creative control as Editor-in-Chief and work with a budget. To put more money towards printing additional full-color spreads, we made the decision to forego mailing the zines and instead hand-delivered each issue from the back of my Jeep Wrangler.</p>
  <p>Below are selected spreads from the final publication.</p>
</div>

